.TH WLA\-SPC700 1 "November 2023" "WLA-DX 10.6" "WLA DX Assembler"
.SH NAME
wla\-spc700 \- WLA DX cross-assembler for the Sony SPC700 (SNES audio CPU)
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B wla\-spc700
.RI [ OPTIONS ]
.B \-o
.I output.o
.I source.asm
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B wla\-spc700
assembles Sony SPC700 source code to a WLA DX object file.
The SPC700 is the audio CPU of the Super Nintendo Entertainment System (SNES),
housed in the Sony SPC700 APU chip.
.PP
All WLA DX assemblers share an identical command-line interface.
For full option descriptions, examples, and a list of all supported CPU
architectures, see
.BR wla\-6502 (1).
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR wla\-6502 (1),
.BR wla\-65816 (1),
.BR wlalink (1)
